::Battera::

Her emotion circuits were going crazy.  Was there a chance that she could be 
going home to Cybertron? She had to take that chance no matter what the 
risks. She wanted to go home so much.  She would just about anything for the 
chance to go home.

"If you will come down from there, perhaps we can talk."

She looked into Scorponoks lab and tried to see the bot inside better. She 
could see tha outline of the bot, but it hid it'self so well that she 
couldn't see a face.
